###  http://www.semanticweb.org/guilhermepinho/ontologies/2026/2/bibliotecas#Biblioteca_Entre_Ontem_e_Amanha
:Biblioteca_Entre_Ontem_e_Amanha rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                          :Biblioteca .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/guilhermepinho/ontologies/2026/2/bibliotecas#Cronos
:Cronos rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                 :Autor ,
                 :Bibliotecario .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/guilhermepinho/ontologies/2026/2/bibliotecas#Linha_T0
:Linha_T0 rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                   :LinhaOriginal .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/guilhermepinho/ontologies/2026/2/bibliotecas#Linha_T1
:Linha_T1 rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                   :LinhaAlternativa .


